Subject: EPP stopped sending logs to our SIEM
Description: We stopped getting logs to our SIEM, QRadar, from EPP. SIEM integration is toggled to on and we haven't made any changes to it. Toggling it on and off did not make any improvements.
What_We_Know__c: performed the steps I received on the escalated ticket and forwarded the results in a Word file to the engineering team
Next_Steps__c: waiting on R&D for the next steps
Solution_Comment__c: issue was on the customer's side, they sent the logs to the wrong address
